What This Library Does

This prompt library supports workflow automation in digital marketing and customer acquisition for Flexikitch. It contains 10 documented, tested, and iterated prompts designed to improve lead generation, nurturing, conversion, and retention.

Each prompt follows a structured format including:

Prompt text (initial + improved)
Workflow task
Problem solved
Automation potential
Risks and limitations
Version history and testing insights

